stateDiagram-v2
    Start --> UnfixedState

    UnfixedState --> MockIncompleteState: FR-REQ-1検出<br/>mkdirSyncモック欠落
    UnfixedState --> PatternMismatchState: FR-REQ-4検出<br/>フォールバック値が旧形式
    UnfixedState --> RecordMissingState: FR-REQ-2,3検出<br/>実装記録欠落
    UnfixedState --> SourceUnknownState: FR-REQ-5検出<br/>権威情報源不明記
    UnfixedState --> ImplementedButMarkedState: FR-REQ-6検出<br/>FIX-1実装済みだが<br/>旧表記が残存

    MockIncompleteState --> MockCompleteState: mkdirSync: vi.fn()<br/>追加実装
    MockCompleteState --> VerifiedState: テスト実行<br/>警告削除確認

    PatternMismatchState --> PatternUpdatedState: パターン更新<br/>/\[#[^\]]{0,50}#\]/g<br/>へ変更
    PatternUpdatedState --> VerifiedState: ビルド・テスト実行<br/>912件以上全合格確認

    RecordMissingState --> RecordAddedState: MEMORY.mdへ<br/>FR-22,FR-A〜FRD<br/>実装記録追記
    RecordAddedState --> VerifiedState: 既存セクション確認

    SourceUnknownState --> SourceDocumentedState: CLAUDE.mdへ<br/>bracketPlaceholderRegex<br/>権威情報源を明記
    SourceDocumentedState --> VerifiedState: 保守ルール動作確認

    ImplementedButMarkedState --> ImplementationMarkedState: MEMORY.mdの<br/>FIX-1セクション見出しを<br/>実装済みに更新
    ImplementationMarkedState --> RootFixDocumentedState: Root fix行を<br/>実装確認済みに更新
    RootFixDocumentedState --> VerifiedState: Workaround残存確認

    VerifiedState --> AllFixesAppliedState: 全修正検証完了<br/>全ファイル確認
    AllFixesAppliedState --> End

